Package com.wolvencraft.yasp.db.tables

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Detailed
    Represents any detailed-type tables in the database.
    Stores table and column names, so that they can be safely used from the plugin
    Hook
    Represents all plugin hook tables in the database.
    Stores table and column names, so that they can be safely used from the plugin
    Normal
    Represents any non-detailed tables in the database.
    Stores table and column names, so that they can be safely used from the plugin
